// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3520 — Mass File Rename (blackbasta)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5f1e8293-2018-59aa-9447-6098d737a988

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
